                Representing Relations
                </summary>
                <details>
                   <summary class="sum2">
                      Introduction
                   </summary>
                   <p>
                     Relations can also be expresed using zero-one matrices
                     and directed graphs. We are considering relations to be
                     binary relations hereon.
                   </p>
                </details>
